{"tid":1785764,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"海外文宣到做展覽又升咗一個層次","createTime":"2019-12-16T15:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T14:50:30.000Z","uid":218761,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac94f52ea3c4dd7ef50b38cbe7df4a1bfccc20f9","tid":1785764,"uid":218761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"推呢個！！！呢班人真係好正<br />\n每隔一陣就放街站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要好慘不時比小粉紅屌 有啲仲比人點相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個其實都忙完讀書就忙戰線大家fol佢個ig支持下佢地啦！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nrepost<br />\n<br />\n呢個展覽係由一班係Nottingham 讀書嘅學生做搞手<br />\n呢一個展覽其實係想俾多啲英國人知道香港發生緊咩事同埋有幾嚴重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個地址喺Nottingham Contemporary<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8v1KovX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8v1KovX.jpg&h=8853a412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度有連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHBa3wL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHBa3wL.jpg&h=0588fb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又有Nottingham嘅人整嘅展品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dreHacZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdreHacZ.jpg&h=5930a3b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有得俾你揀歌聽添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a42tQdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa42tQdt.jpg&h=4a067660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後仲有得攞埋聖誕咭同埋鎖匙扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5hBeFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5hBeFX.jpg&h=adfd5844&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BTgY7D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BTgY7D.png&h=dffd5814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然呢個活動已經完咗 但係都一定會再做過！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d067e68b0f48c1e6f7f6d4f5160e224a8cd5242","tid":1785764,"uid":231342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4dbae5ded9f195d2bb143d92b06190f9041c010","tid":1785764,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"元旦倒數。。年年都係10、9、8、7、6。。。。。<br />\n今年，香港人在全球傳媒鏡頭下，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">10、9、光、復、香、港、時、代、革、命</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.22  聲援新疆集會<br />\n12.24 和你shop 我要攬炒<br />\n12.31 十八區和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1  元旦遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kn972fL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn972fL.jpg&h=d7d2f971&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6TArHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6TArHq.jpg&h=46d9221e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFstMHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFstMHt.jpg&h=85aebd14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSDD8VP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSDD8VP.jpg&h=21442a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcRBVAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcRBVAP.jpg&h=1f846dfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfd75bee817721dbad737d8c3a9c28e32d99860e","tid":1785764,"uid":126054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"多謝英國既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" clas